title: Pr0n4Droid 1.5 aka Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon
description:
Pr0n4Droid is android app for browsing through top porn tube sites.

 - ads free
 - only internet permission is required


 New in version 1.5:

 - added option to hide app from recent apps list
 - added option to protect app with password
 - added media sound is muted when video starts option
 - categories and global "sort by" for search can be configured
 - new sites are added
 - one hand mode optimizations 
 - fix bug with arm64 CPUs
